It might be great to add an optional arguments to the command to get a specific value :

    php app/console container:debug-parameters kernel.root_dir

Could be useful in some cases, for bash scripts:

    $CACHE_DIR="`php app/console container:debug-parameter kernel.cache_dir`/custom-folder"

